                ],
                "institute": "4RUSFEI"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Cascade Generator CG-2.5.",
                "Pneumatic transfer system. The times of sample",
                "transportation from the irradiation position to the",
                "neutron detector were from 150 to 200 ms depending on",
                "gas pressure and the weight of the samples."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "P-T"
                ],
